                </p>
                <p style=" margin-bottom: 10.73px; line-height: 1.1417; text-align: left; margin-left: 0.93px; margin-right: 7.07px; "><span style=" font-size: 14.67px; font-family: 'Rupee Foradian'; ">The minimum rate shall be arrived at as per extant scheme guidelines/ ALCO approved structure.</span>
                </p>
                <p style=" margin-bottom: 10.73px; line-height: 1.1417; text-align: left; margin-left: 0.93px; margin-right: 7.07px; "><span style=" font-size: 14.67px; font-family: 'Rupee Foradian'; ">The rate negotiated with the borrower and reset frequency shall be approved by the sanctioning authority/ Sub Committee of ALCO.</span>
                </p>
                <p style=" margin-bottom: 11.73px; line-height: 1.0792; text-align: left; margin-left: 0.93px; "><span style=" font-size: 14.67px; font-family: 'Rupee Foradian'; ">The approved rate shall be valid for specific period as per approval of the Sanctioning Committee and after that, shall be reviewed/ re-fixed by the sub-committee of the ALCO.</span>
