    <p style=" margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.15; text-align: left; text-indent: 18.93px; "><span
            style=" font-size: 14.67px; font-family: 'Rupee Foradian'; font-style: italic; ">**Since the proposed sanction also includes the amount falling due for repayment in the current limit fixation cycle, the disbursement shall be restricted to a suitable amount to ensure that the actual exposure as on date of disbursement does not exceed the overall exposure limit (set by RiMV including reset at quarterly interval, if any) on the date of each disbursement.</span></p>
